casebody.data:
Russell E. BUCKLEW, petitioner,
v.
MISSOURI. No. 13-10165 (13A1146). Supreme Court of the United States May 21, 2014.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Missouri denied. Order heretofore entered by Justice ALITO vacated.
